{"tid":2057235,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：入股國泰無他想　如果指有政治目的是猜想太多","createTime":"2020-06-09T08:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T01:31:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9cdbebf4182bc5c5bebcc07eada79cb2bda68369","tid":2057235,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波說，動用土地基金投資國泰，是因為基金授權政府有此權力。至於是否繞過立法會，陳茂波以海洋公園注資為例，表示立法會討論需時，加上國泰的大股東太古及國航都是上市公司，討論時會涉及股價敏感資料，因此現時動用土地基金已保障公帑適當運用，但他強調政府已知會立法會有關決定，官員會到立法會接受議員質詢。<br />\n<br />\n被問到國泰在反修例事件期間涉及政治風波，今次政府入股國泰，對公司的管理和營運會否帶來改變。陳茂波回應說，政府入股國泰，別無他想，只是想維護國際航空樞紐的地位，如果指政府是有政治目的，有關考量是猜想太多。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531065-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531065-20200609.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=891fa221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531065-20200609.htm&h=ea372471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531065-20200609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"07b3a061338e0226de948157869019c209d407d8","tid":2057235,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"【國泰重組】英外交密件揭國泰為保97後航權 迫匯豐賣股權予國航<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2057219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2057219</a><br />\n<br />\n?"},{"pid":"7daba9c6044c298943c139c2c7f55b9bdacece03","tid":2057235,"uid":8810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"咁插2個党委入去做乜9？"},{"pid":"dbc0acfb29f7c0cc52d2f006a1690c2b072eb609","tid":2057235,"uid":107297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"此地無銀"},{"pid":"4c9b8baae60d9fa9f25fe9e7f1f35893cd5371eb","tid":2057235,"uid":282637,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:39:19.0